From 26a03731e04fb0bdae335bea0693e0fcc2951f23 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Sat, 30 May 2026 16:42:52 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 63/84] Harden PDF extension boundary

One PDF key now guards the gate,
Fake IDs must simply wait.
Pipes may fail without a crash,
And loose extension trust gets dashed.
